description:
This style aims at switching the position of Appinn's content block and sidebar with additional features:
# wider main content and comment containers;
# move the google ad aside;
# optional slide-open sidebar**;
# the avatars no longer cover the comment text!

**If you have a smaller browsing width like below 1280px, you might feel like a sidebar sliding effect. If so, uncomment the following lines:
/*div#sidebar:hover
 {right: -20px !important;
  -moz-box-shadow: 1px 0px 23px #333;
  -webkit-box-shadow: 1px 0px 23px #333;}*/

--------------------
Appinn 最近的改版让主体内容放在右，而这个样式则是为了把侧边栏放回右边而主体内容和评论放回左边，并添加以下特性：
# 加宽的内容和评论；
# 给广告一个“好一点”的位置；
# 可选的滑动打开侧边栏**；
# 评论者头像不再挡住评论文字了！

**如果你的浏览宽度小于 1280 像素，你可能会喜欢滑动侧边栏，那样的话你只需要把代码中如下几行的注释去掉：
/*div#sidebar:hover
 {right: -20px !important;
  -moz-box-shadow: 1px 0px 23px #333;
  -webkit-box-shadow: 1px 0px 23px #333;}*/

2011.01.17  小众改版。
2011.01.24  小众撤销改版？

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain("www.appinn.com") {

div#wrapper {position: relative !important;}

div#container {float: left !important; width: 90% !important;}

div#container>div>div, #cmt ol li p {width: 90% !important;}

#cmt ol li {width: 100% !important;}

div#sidebar
 {position: absolute !important; right: -220px !important;
  background-color: #F5F3F2 !important;}

div#sidebar:hover
 {right: -20px !important;
  -moz-box-shadow: 1px 0px 23px #333;
  -webkit-box-shadow: 1px 0px 23px #333;}

div#fpost
 {left: 40px !important; top: -292px !important; background-color: #F0E495 !important;}
div#spost {margin-top: 20px !important;}

.topbox span.ilogin {padding: 0 20% 0 0 !important;}

#spost .post {height: auto !important; width: 100% !important;}

div#postfooterinfo>div {width: 49% !important;}

div#wumiiDisplayDiv a {width: 135px !important;}
div#wumiiDisplayDiv a>div {border: none !important;}

#spost a.comments-link {width: 80px !important; background: #E8DDCB !important;}
#spost a.comments-link:before {content: "评论：";}

.gad
{position: absolute !important; right: -100px !important; top: 220px !important; opacity: .3;}

.gad:hover {opacity: 1;}

.entry-content div, .entry-content p {text-align: left !important;}

div#easyTooltip {display: none !important;}

/* not-recommended */ /*
.entry-content .gad, div#sidebar>p {display: none !important;} */
}
